
<div class="ari-page-content-title">Select the rent increase units</div>
<div class="step-description evidence-info-heading">
  <p>Select the specific units for which the rent increase is applicable. For each selected unit, please provide the current monthly rent and the number of tenants that are on or subject to the tenancy agreement. In the next step, you will be required to provide contact information for each of the tenants.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="ari-rent-increase-units-title-container">
